(44, 3, 16, 40, 9, 22, 22, NULL, 'Faith Leading to Wholeness', 'Both passages emphasize the role of faith in achieving healing and wholeness. In Acts, faith in Jesus'' name brings strength, while in Matthew, faith results in being made whole.', 'theme', 0.349, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
