(44, 3, 17, 42, 23, 34, 34, NULL, 'Forgiveness and Ignorance Theme', 'Both passages emphasize the theme of ignorance in wrongdoing. In Acts, Peter acknowledges the ignorance of the people and their rulers, while Jesus, in Luke, asks for forgiveness for those who do not understand their actions.', 'theme', 0.34199999999999997, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
