(44, 3, 18, 42, 24, 44, 44, 'that Christ should suffer', 'Fulfillment of Prophecy', 'This connection highlights the theme of fulfillment in both passages. Acts 3:18 states that Christ''s suffering was foretold by the prophets, while Luke 24:44 emphasizes that all things written in the law and prophets concerning Him must be fulfilled.', 'theme', 0.32799999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
